OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfsted urged to pause      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finspections after teacher  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdeath                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Education unions have called for Ofsted
OL,6, inspections to be paused in the wake of
OL,7, the death of a head teacher.           
OL,9,FRuth Perry, head at Caversham Primary  
OL,10,FSchool in Reading, took her own life   
OL,11,Fwhile waiting for the publication of a 
OL,12,Freport that downgraded her school from 
OL,13,Foutstanding to inadequate.             
OL,15,FThe National Education Union, school   
OL,16,Fleaders' union NAHT and the Association
OL,17,Fof School and College Leaders have     
OL,18,Fcalled for inspections to be halted.   
OL,20,FOfsted has been asked for a comment.   
